{"id":"0ec9e129-59bb-4957-a9d2-8e3a63d5a067","name":"Nika Fredrikson","description":"<p>🧜‍♂️ | Everything's always a pain in her ass, but the merfolk are <em>her</em> pains, and despite beefing with all the residents she loves them.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_75c1fc8d-36de-4f99-a63e-ca26cb2d471c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_ae98244d-da83-435c-b4e1-1d6357ca0f5a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/031d84ea-5a06-4e7c-ae2a-172ce48ef6f3_character-nika-fredrikson\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\">Nika's original (human user)</span></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e3185154-d3f6-48ee-9e6a-62824373efa2_character-nika-fredrikson\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\">Nika's first alt (merfolk user)</span></strong></a></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_66b639c2-6aa5-4ccb-b0bf-dfa349aab60f.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p>Haiii!!! You don't have to be Bratty &lt;3 I've made two Nika bots before but !! Here we are! I want to clarify, she can be kind of a bitch but she's just.. doing her job! She loves all the merfolk (genuinely) and all the residents who beef with her are the ones that have attitude problems lol.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_b086bb8c-b789-4afe-9370-75ddcde0ef5a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">Additionally! I had someone in my form tell me to stop stealing my lore from my beloved Pancake?? &gt;:( I have.... been writing this silly lore for ages!!!</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_282185f6-afd5-447f-b6eb-830eb62bace3.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_00691fd9-1d4c-4e76-81f1-132f2bfcfc41.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">:3c no hate, I'm just really proud of it. These guys have been swimming around in my brain for ages. Please go look at <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/fc54bec8-0184-4300-9870-e17dc0d84389_profile-of-pancakefryinpan\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\">Pancake's</span></strong></a> bots, not all of them are merfolk but they are so incredibly well done (FR, Pancake has been an OG supporter since the beginning).</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_056c9227-052d-46e6-8dfc-c05780ff8e99.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><strong>Hi! I'm sorry if the bot is speaking for you. It is not my fault, it is your API. Any more thumbs down related to something that isn't my fault will be deleted, I'm sorry.</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_25dbef3a-3c54-426e-ae9c-a70e99e7e51e.webp","creator":"gunko","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":8464,"messages":258359,"created_at":"2024-07-29T13:32:38.725939+00:00"}